messages.messageBody:
Greetings!

I just wanted to say thank you..err...domo...for the questions raised and addressed in digest 1392 (samurai 'ranks'). I learned a lot in a short space about the Japanese feudal system. Having an understanding of the Japanese class system of their middle ages, this really illuminated me. Having a degree in (European) Medieval & Renaissance Studies, the comparisons were viable and will help me progress with my Japanese projects.

Thanks again,

Ty
